  "title": "Three people observed a spherical UFO rise vertically in Curitiba-PR [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/30/three-people-observed-a-spherical-ufo-rise-vertically-in-curitiba-pr-1995/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ff",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 17th, 1995</strong>. Time: 05h30 am. Duration: one hour. Three people of the same family observed an unidentified flying object &#8220;moving away from the stars and rising vertically&#8221; for an hour. According to the witness who reported the sighting, the UFO was spherical, &#8220;twice as large as the planet Venus&#8221; as seen in the sky, and &#8220;bright blue&#8221;. The UFO moved &#8220;at 4 km altitude, at. 45° in relation to the observer, and more than 5,000 meters in a straight line, horizontally&#8221;, in the &#8220;northwest position&#8221;. The sighting took place in clear skies and with the naked eye.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.397. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MAY 17th, 1995. Time: 05h30 am. Duration: one hour. Three people of the same family observed an unidentified flying object &#8220;moving away from the stars and rising vertically&#8221; for an hour. According to the witness who reported the sighting, the UFO was spherical, &#8220;twice as large as the planet Venus&#8221; as seen in the sky, [&hellip;]</p>\n",
